    "body": "If an attacker wants to influence the coin flip, instead of spending resources for all 5 blocks, they can only put all of their resources to mine the last block with a block hash that is beneficial for them. Since while mining the last block, the previous 4 block hashes are already mined, public and likely fixed (may change if reorg happens). In that case, `REVEAL` should be just as random as the last block hash.",
